translate spanish brandi8kiss_2e47b5f8:

    # "She leans in and we kiss again, lingering for a while, enjoying the moment."
    "Ella se inclina y nos besamos de nuevo, demorándonos un rato, disfrutando del momento."

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi8.rpy:207
translate spanish brandi8kiss_56324afa:

    # "Her hand touches my chest, rubbing, obviously wanting more than just kissing."
    "Su mano me acaricia el pecho, frotándolo, claramente deseando algo más que solo besos."

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi8.rpy:210
translate spanish brandi8kiss_57ca3c84:

    # "But she pulls away once again."
    "Pero se aparta una vez más."

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi8.rpy:211
translate spanish brandi8kiss_60ae11f7:

    # fd "Oh man. I could get addicted to that."
    fd "Ay, tío. Podría volverme adicto a eso."

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi8.rpy:212
translate spanish brandi8kiss_7d47f573:

    # fd "I don't want to stop, but I want to take it a little slow. One step at a time."
    fd "No quiero parar, pero quiero tomármelo con calma. Paso a paso."

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi8.rpy:213
translate spanish brandi8kiss_6f6de308:

    # fd "Thanks again for coming out with me. I really have to go though."
    fd "Gracias de nuevo por salir conmigo. Aunque de verdad tengo que irme."

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi8.rpy:214
translate spanish brandi8kiss_3898fbf5:

    # pc "Okay, no problem. I'm looking forward to seeing you again."
    pc "Vale, no hay problema. Estoy deseando volver a verte."

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi8.rpy:215
translate spanish brandi8kiss_d026f778:

    # fd "Oh me too. Bye, [pcname]."
    fd "Yo también. Adiós, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi8.rpy:218
translate spanish brandi8kiss_f2567900:

    # "She pays for the meal and we walk out together, then get in our separate cars and drive away."
    "Ella paga la cuenta y salimos juntos, luego nos subimos a nuestros coches respectivos y nos marchamos."

# game/Scenes/Brandi/brandi8.rpy:219
translate spanish brandi8kiss_7bfa1389:

    # "Brandi is fun as always. I really am looking forward to seeing her again."
    "Brandi es tan divertida como siempre. Tengo muchas ganas de volver a verla."

